\begin_layout Itemize
Exclusive disjunction (XOR)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
For exclusive disjunction, the symbol 
\begin_inset Formula $\bigoplus$
\end_inset

 is used.
 Then 
\begin_inset Formula $p\bigoplus q$
\end_inset

 is read as 
\begin_inset Formula $p$
\end_inset

 
\series bold
xor 
\series default

\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

.
 The final value is true if only one of the parent propositions is true.
\end_layout

