\begin_layout Standard
Three more definitions regarding the conditional which are frequently used
 are:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Converse i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $q\rightarrow p$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Inverse i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\sim p\rightarrow\sim q$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Contrapositive i.e.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\sim q\rightarrow\sim p$
\end_inset


\end_layout

